data.title: The 12 Most Unforgettable School Sets In Movies And TV

data.text:
‘Sky High’ – California State University, Northridge

Sky High is a fun superhero coming-of-age film that features a high school several thousand feet in the air training both heroes and sidekicks. The exteriors were shot at the Oviatt Library at California State University, Northridge, which unfortunately doesn’t have any antigravity features in real life.
